snippet.title: Eximius: Seize the Frontline 1.0 Announcement Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
Get ready for the most awesome strategic shooter. One of it's kind of FPS / RTS hybrid. Eximius:Seize the Frontline is exiting early access and launching into 1.0 on March 16th 2021.

Available in Steam & Humble Store

Wishlist now (Steam) : http://store.steampowered.com/app/505740/Eximius_Seize_the_Frontline/
Community : https://discord.gg/ammoboxstudios
